title: Local pre-school benefits from employee volunteers (Milton Keynes Chamber of Commerce Limited)
text: ( Source : Milton Keynes Chamber of Commerce Limited ) One sunny day in August saw a team of 10 employee volunteers complete a community project - they gave a local pre-school garden a much needed makeover. They painted fences and built a play
